&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5 Staff Nurse - Churchill Adult Critical Care &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My name is Clare Morris; I am the unit manager for the Churchill Intensive Care in Oxford. I am privileged to lead our fantastic team of nurses as they deliver care to our patients on the specialist intensive care at the Churchill Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am very keen to hear from you as we have some great opportunities for you, specifically at the Churchill Hospital, to give you a solid start in your intensive care career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in an informal discussion about the staff nurse role and our tailor made critical care foundation programme then I would be very pleased to chat with you about this. You are more than welcome to call on the numbers below or even better, we can make an appointment for me to show you around and answer your questions. Really looking forward to hearing from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clare&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 15th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameClare MorrisJob titleSenior Sister/Unit ManagerEmail addressClare.Morris@ouh.nhs.ukTelephone number01865 235088Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
